{"tid":1369254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑色三毛警告】有兩批人各扮勇武同和理非互相嚴詞攻擊，大家唔好落水！","createTime":"2019-07-26T16:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T00:39:43.000Z","uid":232766,"like":349,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"cda70dab313e6d44bee9fc3f85b621a683c39496","tid":1369254,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"勇武同和理非一剛一柔，<br />\n原本大家討論吓無可厚非，<br />\n反正大家有唔同意見大家都慣，<br />\n一直相安無事，互相尊重、互相支持。<br />\n<br />\n但係今晚突然有兩批人，<br />\n一批扮和理非，一批扮勇武，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一開口就屌老母，<br />\n完全唔係討論，亦唔係勸喻，<br />\n只係透過情緒謾罵煽動兩派敵對！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>佢哋成日提起雨革時兩派嘅分歧，<br />\n想煽動大家互鬥。<br />\n佢哋唔提由自可，一提就令人即刻醒起：<br />\n佢哋呢種分化技倆正正係雨革時嘅常用手段，<br />\n<ins>成個高登就係咁被搞死咗</ins>！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">大家請唔好參與，連負評都唔使，<br />\n做番自己嘢。</span><br />\n<br />\n聽日勇武和理非一齊入元朗。<br />\n大家事前溝通已經好足夠，<br />\n大家都知大家點諗，<br />\n我哋只要互相信任，分化陰謀會自然瓦解！"},{"pid":"88d7dcb334e5ce45c27a16bcca89c7129e574689","tid":1369254,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b0a86efb5f57cae57f798e922469cace82682e54","tid":1369254,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6b0de43c76cda271d75125a1dc4ca406609946c2","tid":1369254,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"20e5ddc944cd6a18f2f8662f71ef594c4694f5ac","tid":1369254,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:05:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7d35e6230508968f5bfa6d651f15f164e6ef113b","tid":1369254,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:06:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c84a1c2f6f0792cc17de2db6ada7dcc8f69656d7","tid":1369254,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:06:34.000Z"