32766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"勇武同和理非一剛一柔，<br />\n原本大家討論吓無可厚非，<br />\n反正大家有唔同意見大家都慣，<br />\n一直相安無事，互相尊重、互相支持。<br />\n<br />\n但係今晚突然有兩批人，<br />\n一批扮和理非，一批扮勇武，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一開口就屌老母，<br />\n完全唔係討論，亦唔係勸喻，<br />\n只係透過情緒謾罵煽動兩派敵對！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>佢哋成日提起雨革時兩派嘅分歧，<br />\n想煽動大家互鬥。<br />\n佢哋唔提由自可，一提就令人即刻醒起：<br />\n佢哋呢種分化技倆正正係雨革時嘅常用手段，<br />\n<ins>成個高登就係咁被搞死咗</ins>！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">大家請唔好參與，連負評都唔使，<br />\n做番自己嘢。</span><br />\n<br />\n聽日勇武和理非一齊入元朗。<br />\n大家事前溝通已經好足夠，<br />\n大家都知大家點諗，<br />\n我哋只要互相信任，分化陰謀會自然瓦解！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db0afbd5ab2e9bf827267e45b788413126c0aa7f","tid":1369254,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53ca3da563a3f9c0881faf1f416671d1f6136347","tid":1369254,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:05:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"429ad3699fe1f3eeb4660a8e6306154bde934fcb","tid":1369254,"uid":279866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:07:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8eecb2c18fa27079c0f41e22a40124cd0fcbf376","tid":1369254,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea4a6dfa387b0da8023b62d3e2cca52821c40f8","tid":1369254,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"其實每次周末夜晚<br />\n當啲手足未番到屋企就已經一堆人出黎互屌<br />\n連仔有無得諗諗負皮1000暫時封ac 2個禮拜"},{"pid":"05a584a42f4dda9425490f51f3f92ab0b8db3ca5","tid":1369254,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:06:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bb5116fe25509776985206be201ab7621f1c389","tid":1369254,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,